nal link to be displayed in the alert message. It can be used to trigger an action.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"onClose","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An optional callback invoked when the close button is clicked. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the close button is not displayed and the alert message","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"remains visible until the context changes (e.g., the issue is resolved, the screen is refreshed). Otherwise, the alert message is dismissable and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"includes a close button, allowing the user to dismiss it when he has acknowledged the message.  Some alerts must remain visible to ensure","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user is aware of important information; others can be closed to reduce visual clutter.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"View\/disabled(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method to have component in disabled state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OUDSAlertMessage(label: \"Success! Your form was submitted.\",","                     status: .positive,","                     bulletList: [","                        AttributedString(\"First thing\"),","                        AttributedString(markdown: \"One **more thing**\"), \/\/ Manage in your side errors for init","                     ])"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"ic_folder_categories.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus":{"title":"OUDSAlertStatus","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus","kind":"sym